List BEDs

Source: R/bedbaser.R
bb_list_beds.Rd

List BEDs

bb_list_beds(api, genome = NULL, bed_type = NULL, limit = 1000, offset = 0)

Arguments

api

API object of BEDbase created from bedbaser()

genome

character() (default NULL) genome keyword

bed_type

character() (default NULL) bed file type

limit

integer() (default 1000) maximum records

offset

integer() (default 0) page token of records

Value

tibble() of BED records

Examples

api <- bedbaser()
bb_list_beds(api)
